  </categoryLinks>
</selectionEntry><selectionEntry id="cd66-6d1f-2db2-6433" name="PaKFront" hidden="false" collective="false" import="true" type="upgrade">
  <profiles>
    <profile id="9aee-cd68-d45e-3064" name="PaKFront" typeId="5cbd-556d-67b5-1bd9" typeName="Command Card" hidden="false">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Gun teams in this Unit cannot Move, but can rotate to face the target when Shooting, and are Nests.Each Gun team is a separate Independent Team.Nest: The Nests are always Concealed and in Bulletproof Cover.Teams attacking a Nest must re-roll successful Firepower tests to Destroy it.Nests cannot Charge into Contact.LFTF: This card can be used with any Gun Unit, including artillery and anti-aircraft guns. Units using this card cannot fire Artillery Bombardments or shoot at Aircraft. Pakfront Nests do not use the Beach Defences rules from the D-Day: American book.LFTF: This costs +2 points per Gun team, rather than +6 points for the Unit.</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Notes" typeId="75a6-20ee-1c76-640a">German, Build, Unit (Gun)</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile id="e660-5213-4e86-580b" name="Forces ID" typeId="86a9-a6ee-b9bd-dafe" typeName="Forces ID" hidden="false">
