  </categoryLinks>
</selectionEntry><selectionEntry id="9d8a-0fa4-bb58-29d1" name="Old Minefields" hidden="false" collective="false" import="true" type="upgrade">
  <profiles>
    <profile id="7609-2786-dc7e-5344" name="Old Minefields" typeId="5cbd-556d-67b5-1bd9" typeName="Command Card" hidden="false">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">In Normandy, the location of minefields was poorly recorded or lost, creating a hazard for troops moving through No-Man&apos;s Land.Before Objectives are placed, place five Old Minefield markers. The players alternate placing markers, starting with this player. Markers must be placed in No-Man&apos;s Land or this Force’s Deployment Area, and at least 4&quot;/10cm apart.When a Team moves within 2&quot;/5cm of an Old Minefield marker, roll a die. On a score of 4+, remove the Old Minefield marker. Otherwise, replace the Old Minefield marker with a Minefield Marker and tests for entering a Minefield as normal.</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Notes" typeId="75a6-20ee-1c76-640a">German, Force, Limited</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile id="b1f5-9f4a-e400-7b19" name="Forces ID" typeId="86a9-a6ee-b9bd-dafe" typeName="Forces ID" hidden="false">
      <characteristics>
