      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">All 8.8cm Heavy AA Platoons in this Force have the following ratings for -1 point per Gun team:
MOTIVATIONCONFIDENT4+Family MenLast Stand 5+
